        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer11890743" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16568538587922077552">I think I once read a more poorly written book. <br/><br/>Let me think for a minute.......hmm........er........uh....... No, I guess I was wrong. <br/><br/>Many books may suck, but few can exceed this one for true crappiness.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


